Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.91,0:25:52.08,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}另人懷念的那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.13,0:25:55.27,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}夢想共鳴著
