Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼 有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計還有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好傷勢沒大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方來正式委託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之今天先好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天出來的診斷結果不錯的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}好漂亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜大人肯定又是第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥...美由？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二年的選舉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當選了學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈當了副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜則當了書記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聚集對我們三個忠實溫順的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結成了以學生會為名目的「白騎士」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快了 很快一切都要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我做到這份上很不可思議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想感謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天看上去都如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是正確的感情表現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 我會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到椅子那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 那個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰 休想壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了軍方的委託太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不用顧及繪理的錢包而大展拳腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明從來就沒有顧及過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以後幹什麼都不用負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 可以毫無顧忌地行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能快速解決事件了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes！能解開謎底＆完美救出美少女們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 現在設備也萬全了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？設備？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關鎗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不過人家說「沒有許可不準開槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然裝上了就要開槍呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們啊 不洗澡就開不成會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身心都坦誠相對的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來護衛都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們可以捲鋪蓋回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能不能幫我照看那孩子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來啊 繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在可以功成身退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想奪走我的神秘謎團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 就算老天放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真海繪理也不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 我明白了 把前面遮一遮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 別亂來啊 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都大鬧過一場了 竟然還若無其事地過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒事的話 就回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續妨礙我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命不保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 現在到哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到正上方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好高 好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐步降低高度 開始進行探測
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方還借了些拉風的「玩具」給我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 地底探測裝置值多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 給我認真拍好啊 要清晰無碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是在拍寫真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花憐 前往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 學姐也開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 學姐 請多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟樣子已經被人見過一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 因為我已經進行了完美的變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能控制 跟上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有一瞬間 但是操場有條發光的線般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料洩漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要關掉引擎迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫降？你降去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華平安著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我這邊繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜堂 操場 還有體育館的地下有構造物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當有規模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是設施 到底是用來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 就是巨型機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七神合體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在電視購物上買到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認真說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是巨型宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外星人在誘拐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是美少女失蹤事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了調查這個星球的生態系統 美少女們才會被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看到的就是其中一種Cattle Mutilation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(*Cattle Mutilation 牛隻肢體被切除 多被認為是外星人進行的實驗)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 神秘事件狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那裡沒人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一隻老鼠都沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房間裡面什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我也不知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去 就像是搬走了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 沒有地方破損
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長射擊造成的彈痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老師強行闖入的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都消失得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不在禮拜堂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去體育館看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Silver Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行B計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉接高雷準將閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往地下的入口...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有的 就在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不戰鬥就跑 很讓人介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是陷阱...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要闖一闖！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了 繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪理？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下無法通信麼...這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 藍華 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 這可不是到了地下就會被隔斷的通信器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人為干擾麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華的聯絡中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為你們的同伴的話身體能力會得到強化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有生體認證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是那麼的過激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.07,0:24:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.41,0:24:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能來到這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.90,0:26:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.33,0:26:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要結束的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.54,0:26:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.36,0:26:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero？


